== Gloria kamanzi uwizera ==
Gloria kamanzi uwizera ni umunyarwandakazi  akaba ari we washinze '''Glo creations Ltd''' ndetse akaba n'umunyamuryango wa Women Entrepreneurship programme(AWEP Rwanda)<ref>http://m.igihe.com/serivisi/special-pages/womens-month/inkuru/article/uwizera-washinze-glo-creations-afite-inzozi-zo-kugira-uruganda-rukora-ibitenge</ref> .

== Umwuga ==
Gloria kamanzi uwizera yatangije Glo creations Ltd muri 2008 iherereye mu Kiyovu, aho akora imyambaro n'imitako yo mu nzu<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/lifestyle/textile-designer-12-year-long-journey</ref>. Yifashisha  batik akaba ari uburyo akoresha akora ibihangano bye akoresheje amaboko<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/lifestyle/textile-designer-12-year-long-journey</ref>.

